<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="color-scheme" content="only light">
<meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light">
<title>Sunshine Fortune Buildtech — Built to Hold</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --concrete: #FFFFFF;
    --concrete-dark: #F4F4F4;
    --charcoal: #101010;
    --charcoal-soft: #2B302B;
    --steel: #2B5578;
    --steel-light: #6C8CA8;
    --amber: #D98A1E;
    --rebar: #3F3F3F;
    --line: rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.12);
  }

  html {
    background: #FFFFFF !important;
    color-scheme: only light;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
    *, *::before, *::after {
      animation-duration: 0.001ms !important;
      animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
      transition-duration: 0.001ms !important;
      scroll-behavior: auto !important;
    }
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: #FFFFFF;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  h1, h2, h3, .display {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }

  .mono {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  a { color: inherit; }

  .wrap {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }

  .hazard-bar {
    height: 8px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      -45deg,
      var(--charcoal), var(--charcoal) 14px,
      var(--amber) 14px, var(--amber) 28px
    );
  }

  /* ---------- Blueprint grid backdrop ---------- */
  .blueprint {
    position: relative;
    background-color: #FFFFFF;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--line) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--line) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 42px 42px;
  }

  /* ---------- Header ---------- */
  header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 50;
    background: var(--concrete);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
  }
  .nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 18px 32px;
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .brand .mark {
    display: inline-flex;
    width: 30px; height: 30px;
    background: var(--amber);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .brand .mark span { transform: rotate(-45deg); }
  .brand small {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--rebar);
    text-transform: none;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  nav.links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 34px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  nav.links a {
    text-decoration: none;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }
  nav.links a:hover { border-color: var(--amber); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--concrete);
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--steel); }
  .menu-btn { display: none; }

  /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
  .hero {
    padding: 96px 32px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: end;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--steel);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before {
    content: "";
    width: 28px; height: 2px;
    background: var(--amber);
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(44px, 6vw, 84px);
    line-height: 0.98;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--steel);
  }
  .hero p.lead {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: normal;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--charcoal-soft);
    max-width: 42ch;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .hero-cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 36px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--concrete);
    padding: 16px 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--steel); }
  .btn-secondary {
    padding: 16px 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    border: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--steel); color: var(--steel); }

  /* Measurement panel — signature element */
  .measure-panel {
    border: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
    background: var(--concrete-dark);
    padding: 28px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .measure-panel::before {
    content: "SITE DATA";
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 24px;
    background: var(--amber);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 3px 10px;
  }
  .measure-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--line);
  }
  .measure-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .measure-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--rebar);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .measure-value {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .measure-value sup {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--steel);
    margin-left: 2px;
  }
  .measure-progress {
    margin-top: 20px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--concrete);
    border: 1px solid var(--charcoal);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .measure-progress .bar {
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      -45deg,
      var(--amber), var(--amber) 8px,
      var(--charcoal) 8px, var(--charcoal) 16px
    );
  }
  .measure-caption {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--rebar);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ---------- Marquee strip ---------- */
  .strip {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--concrete);
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
  }
  .strip-track {
    display: flex;
    white-space: nowrap;
    animation: scroll-left 34s linear infinite;
    width: max-content;
  }
  .strip-track span {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 14px 36px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--concrete);
  }
  .strip-track span::before { content: "◆"; color: var(--amber); font-size: 10px; }
  @keyframes scroll-left {
    from { transform: translateX(0); }
    to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }

  /* ---------- Sections shared ---------- */
  section { padding: 100px 0; }
  .section-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .section-head h2 {
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 46px);
    font-weight: 600;
    max-width: 16ch;
  }
  .section-head p {
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: normal;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    color: var(--rebar);
    max-width: 38ch;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  /* ---------- Process (real sequence: build phases) ---------- */
  .phases {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
  }
  .phase {
    padding: 32px 28px;
    border-right: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
    position: relative;
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
  }
  /* JS enhances with a reveal animation; CSS alone always shows full content. */
  .phase.js-reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(16px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .phase.in-view { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .phase:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .phase .num {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--amber);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .phase h3 {
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .phase p {
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: normal;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--rebar);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  /* ---------- Services ---------- */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    background: var(--charcoal);
    border: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
  }
  .service-card {
    background: var(--concrete);
    padding: 36px 30px;
    transition: background 0.25s ease;
  }
  .service-card:hover { background: var(--concrete-dark); }
  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .service-card p {
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: normal;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--rebar);
  }
  .service-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--steel);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ---------- Projects ---------- */
  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .project-card {
    border: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
    background: var(--concrete-dark);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .project-swatch {
    height: 160px;
    position: relative;
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, var(--steel-light) 0 2px, transparent 2px 14px),
      var(--steel);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 16px 18px;
  }
  .project-swatch .icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: var(--concrete);
    border: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .project-swatch .swatch-tag {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--concrete);
    background: rgba(28,32,29,0.55);
    padding: 5px 10px;
  }
  .project-swatch.b {
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, #C9BEA2 0 2px, transparent 2px 14px),
      var(--rebar);
  }
  .project-swatch.c {
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, #F0C67D 0 2px, transparent 2px 14px),
      var(--amber);
  }
  .project-swatch.c .swatch-tag { color: var(--charcoal); background: rgba(234,231,224,0.75); }
  .project-body { padding: 22px 24px; }
  .project-body .mono {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--rebar);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .project-body h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .project-body p {
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: normal;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--rebar);
  }

  /* ---------- Stats band ---------- */
  .stats-band {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    text-align: left;
  }
  .stat {
    padding: 0 24px;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(234,231,224,0.18);
  }
  .stat:first-child { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; }
  .stat .num {
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--amber);
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .stat .unit { font-size: 18px; color: var(--concrete); }
  .stat .label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(234,231,224,0.85);
    margin-top: 8px;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ---------- CTA ---------- */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--concrete);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-box {
    border: 2px solid var(--charcoal);
    padding: 72px 40px;
    background: var(--concrete-dark);
    position: relative;
  }
  .cta-box::before, .cta-box::after {
    content: "+";
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }
  .cta-box::before { top: -13px; left: -13px; }
  .cta-box::after { bottom: -13px; right: -13px; }
  .cta-box h2 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
    max-width: 22ch;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }
  .cta-box p {
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: normal;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    color: var(--rebar);
    max-width: 46ch;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  /* ---------- Footer ---------- */
  footer {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--concrete);
    padding: 56px 32px 28px;
  }
  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(234,231,224,0.16);
  }
  footer h4 {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--amber);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  footer ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  footer li { margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; }
  footer a { text-decoration: none; opacity: 1; color: var(--concrete); }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--amber); }
  .footer-bottom {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding-top: 24px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: rgba(234,231,224,0.85);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  /* ---------- Responsive ---------- */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav.links, .nav-cta { display: none; }
    .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .phases { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .phase:nth-child(2) { border-right: none; }
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .projects-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); row-gap: 32px; }
    .stat:nth-child(3) { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; row-gap: 32px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .hero { padding: 64px 20px 56px; }
    .wrap { padding: 0 20px; }
    section { padding: 64px 0; }
    .phases { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .phase { border-right: none; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  :focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid var(--steel);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="nav">
      <div class="brand">
        <span class="mark"><span>SF</span></span>
        <div>
          SUNSHINE FORTUNE
          <div><small>BUILDTECH &nbsp;/&nbsp; EST. SITE OPS</small></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <nav class="links">
        <a href="#process">Process</a>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <a class="nav-cta" href="#contact">Request a Quote</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hazard-bar" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero blueprint">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">Design–Build Contractor</div>
        <h1>We pour the <em>foundation</em>.<br>You get the credit.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Sunshine Fortune Buildtech runs commercial and industrial builds end to end — permits, structure, mechanical, finish — delivered on the date we quoted, not the date we hoped for.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta-row">
          <a class="btn-primary" href="#contact">Start a Project →</a>
          <a class="btn-secondary" href="#services">See What We Do</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="measure-panel">
        <div class="measure-row">
          <span class="measure-label">Scope</span>
          <span class="measure-value" style="font-size:18px;">New Build &amp; Renovation</span>
        </div>
        <div class="measure-row">
          <span class="measure-label">Sectors</span>
          <span class="measure-value" style="font-size:18px;">Commercial · Industrial</span>
        </div>
        <div class="measure-row">
          <span class="measure-label">Coverage</span>
          <span class="measure-value" style="font-size:18px;">Structure to Finish</span>
        </div>
        <div class="measure-row">
          <span class="measure-label">Contact</span>
          <span class="measure-value" style="font-size:18px;">Manoj Kumar Gupta</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="strip" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="strip-track">
      <span>Commercial Fit-Out</span>
      <span>Steel &amp; Concrete Structure</span>
      <span>Site Excavation</span>
      <span>Mechanical &amp; Electrical</span>
      <span>Permit Management</span>
      <span>Renovation &amp; Retrofit</span>
      <span>Commercial Fit-Out</span>
      <span>Steel &amp; Concrete Structure</span>
      <span>Site Excavation</span>
      <span>Mechanical &amp; Electrical</span>
      <span>Permit Management</span>
      <span>Renovation &amp; Retrofit</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section id="process">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>Four phases. Same crew, start to finish.</h2>
        <p>No handoffs between subcontractors who've never met. One team owns the site from groundbreak to walkthrough.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="phases wrap" style="padding-left:0; padding-right:0;">
      <div class="phase">
        <span class="num">PH.01</span>
        <h3>Survey &amp; Permit</h3>
        <p>Site assessment, soil testing, and permit filing before a single stake goes in the ground.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="phase">
        <span class="num">PH.02</span>
        <h3>Foundation &amp; Structure</h3>
        <p>Excavation, footings, and structural frame — concrete, steel, or timber, engineered to spec.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="phase">
        <span class="num">PH.03</span>
        <h3>Systems &amp; Envelope</h3>
        <p>MEP rough-in, insulation, and building envelope closed before weather becomes a variable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="phase">
        <span class="num">PH.04</span>
        <h3>Finish &amp; Handover</h3>
        <p>Interior finish, punch list, and a walkthrough where you find nothing left to flag.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>What we take off your plate</h2>
        <p>Scoped, quoted, and scheduled — each service can run standalone or as part of a full build.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
